name: La-region-library-map
tagline: Map of all the libraries in the LA region.
body:
### Introduction
LA County is a huge area and has a lot of libraries - let's put them all on a map!

### Contribute
See something that's wrong?  Have a feature suggestion?  Are we missing data?  Open an [Issue](https://github.com/matikin9/la-region-library-map/issues)!

### Contact
If you have a question or comment, feel free to open an Issue or email me at nina@ninakin.com.
